{"tid":1638502,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"自認係中國人既手足割唔割？","createTime":"2019-10-08T10:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T12:39:33.000Z","uid":181156,"like":25,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b1e30198e3d526877ffe2c2f64af60990579585e","tid":1638502,"uid":181156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:35:02.000Z","msg":"朋友叫我幫手出po<br />\n佢係深黃，一直以黎都有去發夢，好努力幫手做文宣<br />\n佢眼見依家好多人都唔止同中共，係要同中國割，佢絕對唔係反對手足們有呢個諗法，但係佢自己大學讀中國文學，好熱愛中華文化（e.g詩詞歌賦)，亦唔否認自己係大中華膠<br />\n<br />\n佢同大家一樣好憎中共，但好愛中華民族，老土啲講係愛國不愛黨<br />\n<br />\n佢淨係想問一問大家，對於呢啲人會唔會割？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4dc036d5c0f3fcdad2b66a5fb3d594372b3bcf6","tid":1638502,"uid":181156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:35:25.000Z","msg":"就算割都會繼續發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec8aff11a01b8fb9ad3974d0ae3e09943ea7434","tid":1638502,"uid":181156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:36:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3287c2f9b84fe7d7f71346f507eb35ac85e4840b","tid":1638502,"uid":187950,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:38:28.000Z","msg":"唔割 反共既就自己友<br />\n不過希望佢唔好再大中華膠<br />\n共=/=國"},{"pid":"b2966d005b0521bf589acdb6c9a839fe7f5dd318","tid":1638502,"uid":144943,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:38:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e87f9bcafe35b2b8aa5890fa8834e557601e74","tid":1638502,"uid":181156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3287c2f9b84fe7d7f71346f507eb35ac85e4840b","tid":1638502,"uid":187950,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:38:28.000Z","msg":"唔割 反共既就自己友<br />\n不過希望佢唔好再大中華膠<br />\n共=/=國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:38:52.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1945f3669b3f74403d433c4bf7e55b868f9